{"tid":2442974,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人間傑尼龜！Brave Girls侑廷「微肉身材＋笑眼」融化韓網：別減肥 |","createTime":"2021-03-11T18:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T03:44:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bba40b175645092bffa0530291565b988975d2b1","tid":2442974,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"南韓女團Brave Girls由知名製作人「勇敢兄弟」培養後於2011年推出，隨後歷經了數次成員變動，始終未能成名。然而近日2017年發行的中毒歌曲《Rollin》突然因為「留言集錦」影片於韓網掀起熱議，睽違4年逆行攻佔所有音源榜第一，團體被「強制召喚」回鍋上音樂節目，其中成員侑廷的直拍吸引了許多網友、粉絲留言熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5499/d5499081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5499%2Fd5499081.jpg&h=d69b69b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Brave Girls被召回音樂節目。（圖／翻攝Brave Girls官方IG）<br />\n<br />\nBrave Girls侑廷在先前的「留言集錦」影片中，便有許多網友曾表示喜歡她清爽、甜美的笑容，稱讚「讓人看了也會感受到幸福」，因此圈了許多粉絲，11日團體登上音樂《M Countdown》表演《Rollin》，隨後官方也將4位成員的直拍影片上傳，其中侑廷的影片觀看數大大領先其他團的直拍，底下也湧入網友熱烈討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5499/d5499082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5499%2Fd5499082.jpg&h=58146e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲侑廷直拍引發討論。（圖／翻攝YouTube／M2）<br />\n<br />\n侑廷的直拍下方網友紛紛留言稱讚「緊張的傑尼龜本尊，連拉露肚臍上衣的樣子也好可愛」、「我如果是男人一定會著迷，身材很好、笑眼也好有魅力，現存偶像中笑起來最好看」、「真的是貝果女代表，超美」、「笑眼超美，看了心情跟著好起來」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5499/d5499080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5499%2Fd5499080.jpg&h=1a31692e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲侑廷撞臉神奇寶貝中的「傑尼龜」。（圖／翻攝侑廷IG）<br />\n<br />\n雖然侑廷身材曲線火辣，但由於其他線上女偶像都偏瘦，因此有部分人認為她「有點太肉」，然而，這類的留言出現後，馬上冒出更多的網友霸氣回嗆「比起其他瘦巴巴的偶像更喜歡這樣有肉的！身材非常完美」、「禁止姐姐減肥，希望不要因為看到那些人的留言就走心」、「不准勇兄要求她們減肥，Brave Girls現在不是你的是全國民的」，足以見得她的火紅的人氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oid111KKPNA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Doid111KKPNA&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=ad57ca88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oid111KKPNA</a>"},{"pid":"2d4a8239d2946900e4a797ac7e1d4a9d835c109c","tid":2442974,"uid":320858,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"係幾正<br />\nPo多呢啲咪好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88437946143836f1e2018e61479cef096cded27","tid":2442974,"uid":2781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T00:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtEQvg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtEQvg3.jpg&h=2aa23b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nall kill埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2feacfdc3ec7de7265a3dd9e4ef7f1192d003a1","tid":2442974,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T00:04:36.000Z","msg":"係咪好似以前exid咁?"},{"pid":"a5e3179f5268fbc72926de185e95e31118b074f3","tid":2442974,"uid":342990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T00:06:05.000Z","msg":"有冇整容前嘅相？"},{"pid":"334d13284e8293272c5baf424d5dc9d1cf641f97","tid":2442974,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d88437946143836f1e2018e61479cef096cded27","tid":2442974,"uid":2781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T00:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtEQvg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtEQvg3.jpg&h=2aa23b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nall kill埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T00:15:45.000Z","msg":"係Perfect All Kill"},{"pid":"9bf66d3779a27ec266b4d7e2326ecca514187b6e","tid":2442974,"uid":68678,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T00:27:02.000Z","msg":"不啦 成班老女人 <br />\n#izoneforever"},{"pid":"0761db7f5dc1605d7849b59f3f0b6f2d40d772d2","tid":2442974,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc